metadata.name: ‏Losses !
metadata.description:
Sometimes my hands take the place of my
‏ eyes and cries from my insides from my fingertips
‏ drop
‏ drop
‏ drop
‏ they fall
‏ Those calls that I have not answered
‏ Screams that I did not say
‏ The ways I did not go
‏ The kisses I didn't get
‏ All that did not happen
‏ It fell from my fingers …
